data.description: This Beautiful Home Has Been Loved By The Same Family for Over 20 Years! This 2 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom Townhouse is Turnkey! NEW ROOF (2023), AC (2015, still under warranty), NEW Water Heater (2023), NEW Kitchen and Bathroom Vanities, NEW Paint Throughout, and BRAND NEW Stainless Steel Kitchen Appliances (Refrigerator, Range, Microwave, and Dishwasher). The Floor Plan Features a Great Room that Includes a Dining Area. Master has a Walk-In Shower and Spacious Closet. Very Large 2nd Bedroom and Full Guest Bath. Large Florida Room with additional Closet Space. Washer and Dryer convey as well. This Home comes with 2 parking spaces as well as a shelved carport storage room. Quiet Neighborhood yet Convenient Access to The FL Turnpike, Hwy 192, Orlando Int’l Airport, Area Attractions, Schools, Shopping, Restaurants and More. This Home Has Been Beautifully Maintained and Is Ready for New Owners!
